<section id="vision" class="row">

  <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1">
    <h1 class="col-xs-12"
      data-300="margin-top: 0;" 
      data-500="margin-top: -20px;">
        Let's create a world where we can fall back in love with learning and teaching.
    </h1>
  </div>

  <div class='col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-sm-offset-1'>
    <div class="col-xs-12">
      <h2>Chalkle’s Backstory</h2>

      <p>
        Chalkle started over a cup of coffee between Silvia Zuur and Linc Gasking in mid 2012. A whirlwind of community organising followed, and Chalkle exploded in Wellington, with Silvia organising over 600 classes in 12 months to serve a world where ‘anyone could teach and anyone could learn’.
      </p>
      <p>
        Demand grew, the business evolved, technology was built. Now, with the same spirit of ‘anyone can...’ Chalkle is supporting educators with software tools and a marketing platform.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-sm-6 first-coffee">
    <%= image_tag asset_path("partners/first-coffee.jpg") %>
  </div>

</section>

